                                                        </p>
                                                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><span>At the moment we have
                                                                two open positions for the <strong>Trust Fundraiser Position </strong>(Kenya and Peru Programme)
                                                            </span><span></span></p>
                                                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal"><span>This internship is ideal
                                                                for a recent graduate looking to develop useful fundraising work experience in the third sector
                                                                and a small NGO environment. The ideal candidate should possess sufficient knowledge and skills
                                                                to enable them to operate independently with very limited technical support and
                                                                supervision.<strong> </strong></span></p>
                                                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
                                                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal" class="MsoNormal">
                                                            <span><strong>Responsibilities:</strong> </span></p>
                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
                                                                style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol"><span><span
                                                                        style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span
                                                                style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Helping
                                                                develop, implement and monitor fundraising campaigns and appeals.</span></p>
                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
                                                                style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol"><span><span
                                                                        style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span
                                                                style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Research,
                                                                profile and liaise with appropriate donor bases, including individuals, trusts and statutory
                                                                sources.</span></p>
                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
                                                                style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol"><span><span
                                                                        style="font: 7pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span
                                                                style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Drafting grant
                                                                applications for Trust and Foundations. </span></p>
                                                        <p style="margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt" class="MsoListParagraph"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span
